            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "$validator = new Zend_Validate_Float(array('locale' => 'en_US'));\r\nZend_Debug::dump($validator->isValid('0,66')); ->> print false - that's correct\r\nZend_Debug::dump($validator->isValid('0.66')); ->> print true - that's correct as well\r\nbut\r\nZend_Debug::dump($validator->isValid('0,666')); ->> print true - that's INCORRECT, should be false"
